title: Arnette at the VolcomPipePro
description:
Congrats to Mason Ho for taking 3rd in the 2014 Volcom Pipe Pro and winning the Todd Chesser Award!

Surfers in order of appearance: Fred Pattachia, Joel Centio, Mason Ho, Parker Coffin

Music: "Six O'Clock"
The Rustangs
